name: 188-microphone-recording-outline

description: 1,2,3... we're on! Welcome to the episode of iconic Animations. This animated icon represents a microphone recording.

description: Let's mute for a second and think again about what we want to say. This animated icon represents a muted microphone.

name: 190-microphone-stop-recording-button-morph-outline

description: Let's wrap it up! Come back for another episode of Animated Greatness! This animated icon represents a microphone.

name: 22-play-pause-morph-outline
title: Play & Pause
description: Take a pause and enjoy the content as you like! This animated icon stands for the pause button.

description: Let's play it by ear! What song are you listening to next? This animated icon stands for a play button.

description: Thank you, next! Let's move forward. This animated icon represents a 'play forward' button.

description: Let's listen to our song again, shall we? This animated icon stands for a “double playback” button.
